Dragon Herald			KEY:Bard Archetype ~ Dragon Herald										CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.BardArchetype.BardArmorProficiencies.BardWeaponProficiencies.BardBardicKnowledge.BardCounterSong.BardFascinate.BardInspireCompetence.BardSoothingPerformance.BardInspireHeroics.BardLoreMaster.BardJackOfAllTrades	PRECLASS:1,Bard=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Bard Archetype ~ Dragon Herald],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.BardArmorProficiencies,TYPE.BardWeaponProficiencies,TYPE.BardBardicKnowledge,TYPE.BardCounterSong,TYPE.BardFascinate,TYPE.BardInspireCompetence,TYPE.BardSoothingPerformance,TYPE.BardInspireHeroics,TYPE.BardLoreMaster,TYPE.BardJackOfAllTrades]																																	DESC:Dragon heralds are messengers and evangelists of true dragonkind. They carry the word of their dragon patrons far and wide, whether that's a message of peace or a declaration of war. A kobold whose scales already associate her with a revered dragon is often trained as her tribe's dragon herald.																																																																																												ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Herald ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency|PRECLASS:1,Bard=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Herald ~ Dragon Patron|PRECLASS:1,Bard=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Herald ~ Coat of Arms|PRECLASS:1,Bard=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Herald ~ Dragon Voice|PRECLASS:1,Bard=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Herald ~ Diplomatic Immunity|PRECLASS:1,Bard=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Herald ~ Diplomatic Protection|PRECLASS:1,Bard=3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Herald ~ Rebuke Foes|PRECLASS:1,Bard=12	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Herald ~ Retreat to Lair|PRECLASS:1,Bard=15	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Herald ~ Master of Persuasion|PRECLASS:1,Bard=5	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dragon Herald ~ Extol Glory|PRECLASS:1,Bard=10																																									