Weapon and Armor Proficiency	KEY:Dragon Herald ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Bard Class Features.SpecialQuality.BardArmorProficiencies.BardWeaponProficiencies																																																																																																																					DESC:The dragon herald is proficient with simple weapons and light armor, but not with shields. Dragon heralds are mes sengers, not warriors. Like other bards, dragon heralds don't incur the normal arcane spell failure chance from wearing light armor.																																																																																																AUTO:WEAPONPROF|TYPE.Simple	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|TYPE=ArmorProfLight																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Dragon Patron			KEY:Dragon Herald ~ Dragon Patron										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Bard Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																										DESC:A dragon herald must choose a particular true dragon species whose glory to extol. In most cases, this is a dragon with whom the herald is familiar, but it could be a dragon deity, a long-dead dragon hero, or even an entire dragon lineage. The energy type associated with her dragon patron determines the energy type used by several of her abilities. She must also designate a sacred space relevant to her dragon choice-usually the lair of a patron dragon or a shrine or holy place associated with a dragon type.																																																																																																																																																																																																											BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Dragon Herald Patron|1																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Coat of Arms			KEY:Dragon Herald ~ Coat of Arms										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Bard Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																										DESC:A dragon herald gains energy resistance %1 against |BardLVL	DESC:acid.|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Acid,1	DESC:electricity.|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Electricity,1	DESC:cold.|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Cold,1	DESC:fire.|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Fire,1	DESC: This resistance stacks with any inherent racial resistances, but not with magical or temporary resistances.																																																																														ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Resistance to Acid|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Acid,1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Resistance to Cold|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Cold,1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Resistance to Electricity|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Electricity,1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Resistance to Fire|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Fire,1																																																																																																								BONUS:VAR|AcidResistanceBonus|BardLVL|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Acid,1	BONUS:VAR|ColdResistanceBonus|BardLVL|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Cold,1	BONUS:VAR|ElectricityResistanceBonus|BardLVL|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Electricity,1	BONUS:VAR|FireResistanceBonus|BardLVL|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Fire,1								SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Dragon Voice			KEY:Dragon Herald ~ Dragon Voice										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Bard Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.BardBardicKnowledge																																																																																																																							DESC:A dragon herald gains a +%1 bonus on Intimidate and Diplomacy checks. She gains Draconic as a bonus language.|floor(BardLVL/2)																																																																																																																AUTO:LANG|Draconic																																																																																																																																																																			BONUS:SKILL|Intimidate,Diplomacy|floor(BardLVL/2)																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Diplomatic Immunity		KEY:Dragon Herald ~ Diplomatic Immunity									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Bard Class Features.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.BardCounterSong.BardFascinate																																																																																																																					DESC:A dragon herald can use bardic performance to generate a sanctuary effect upon herself. Most use this to deliver the word of their patron or to safely complete Diplomacy or Intimidate checks in the presence of hostile foes. The effect persists for as long as the dragon herald performs and for 1 round after.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Diplomatic Protection		KEY:Dragon Herald ~ Diplomatic Protection									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Bard Class Features.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.BardInspireCompetence																																																																																																																							DESC:The dragon herald can use bardic performance to wrap a single ally in the colors and scales of her patron. The dragon herald must be able to see her ally, and that ally must be able to perceive her performance. While the herald performs, the target gains a +%1 enhancement bonus to natural armor and resistance %2 against |floor(BardLVL/2)|BardLVL*2	DESC:acid.|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Acid,1	DESC:electricity.|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Electricity,1	DESC:cold.|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Cold,1	DESC:fire.|PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Fire,1																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Rebuke Foes				KEY:Dragon Herald ~ Rebuke Foes										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Bard Class Features.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.BardSoothingPerformance																																																																																																																						DESC:The dragon herald gains the ability to rain down her patron's wrath on her enemies, dealing %1 |BardLVL*2	DESC:acid |PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Acid,1	DESC:electricity |PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Electricity,1	DESC:cold |PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Cold,1	DESC:fire |PREVARGTEQ:DragonHeraldPatron_Fire,1	DESC:damage (Reflex save for half). She can target %1 enemies within 50 feet. This effect occurs once per round for as long as she continues her performance.|floor(BardLVL/4)																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Retreat to Lair			KEY:Dragon Herald ~ Retreat to Lair										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Bard Class Features.SpecialQuality.SpellLike.BardInspireHeroics																																																																																																																								DESC:The dragon herald can spend 5 daily uses of performance as a full-round action to teleport herself, or a willing target touched, to her sacred place.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Master of Persuasion		KEY:Dragon Herald ~ Master of Persuasion									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Bard Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.BardLoreMaster																																																																																																																								DESC:The dragon herald becomes so sure in her craft that she can take 10 on any Diplomacy or Intimidate check, even when rushed or threatened. She may attempt either a Diplomacy or Intimidate check as a full-round action	DESC: once a day, instead of spending a full minute.|PREVARLT:BardLVL,11	DESC: twice a day, instead of spending a full minute.|PREVARGTEQ:BardLVL,11|PREVARLT:BardLVL,17	DESC: three times a day, instead of spending a full minute.|PREVARGTEQ:BardLVL,17																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.23
