Swarm Fighter			KEY:Fighter Archetype ~ Swarm Fighter			CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.FighterArchetype.FighterArmorProficiencies.FighterBonusFeat1.FighterBravery.FighterBonusFeat2.FighterBonusFeat6.FighterBonusFeat10.FighterBonusFeat14.FighterBonusFeat18.FighterArmorTraining1.FighterArmorTraining2.FighterArmorTraining3.FighterArmorTraining4.FighterWeaponMastery												PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Fighter Archetype ~ Swarm Fighter],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.FighterArmorProficiencies,TYPE.FighterBonusFeat1,TYPE.FighterBravery,TYPE.FighterBonusFeat2,TYPE.FighterBonusFeat6,TYPE.FighterBonusFeat10,TYPE.FighterBonusFeat14,TYPE.FighterBonusFeat18,TYPE.FighterArmorTraining1,TYPE.FighterArmorTraining2,TYPE.FighterArmorTraining3,TYPE.FighterArmorTraining4,TYPE.FighterWeaponMastery]	DESC:Kobolds know there's strength in numbers, and they rarely send fewer than two kobolds out on patrol. This reliance on one another extends to combat tactics too - overwhelming numbers and tight quarters are the kobold fighter's friends. Scuttling between the legs of friend and foe alike, the swarm fighter is an unshakable combatant.																																								ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Swarm Fighter ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Swarm Fighter ~ Athletic Prowess|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Swarm Fighter ~ Mobility|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Swarm Fighter ~ Safety in Numbers|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Swarm Fighter ~ Bonus Teamwork Feats|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Swarm Fighter ~ Bonus Feats|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Swarm Fighter ~ Share Space|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=5	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Swarm Fighter ~ Strike the Underbelly|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=9	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Swarm Fighter ~ Always Underfoot|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=13	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Swarm Fighter ~ Soft Underbelly|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=20																																																									COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.23	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Fighter

Weapon and Armor Proficiency	KEY:Swarm Fighter ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Fighter Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterArmorProficiencies																																																																																																																										DESC:A swarm fighter is proficient with all simple and martial weapons. She is proficient with light and medium armor, but not with shields.																																																											AUTO:ARMORPROF|ARMORTYPE=ArmorProfLight	AUTO:ARMORPROF|ARMORTYPE=ArmorProfMedium																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Athletic Prowess			KEY:Swarm Fighter ~ Athletic Prowess			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Fighter Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																															DESC:A swarm fighter adds Acrobatics and Climb to her class skills, and gains a +%1 bonus on checks with these skills.|floor(FighterLVL/2)																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						BONUS:SKILL|Acrobatics|floor(FighterLVL/2)	BONUS:SKILL|Climb|floor(FighterLVL/2)														CSKILL:Acrobatics	CSKILL:Climb			SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Mobility				KEY:Swarm Fighter ~ Mobility					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Fighter Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterBonusFeat1																																																																																																																												DESC:The swarm fighter gains Mobility as a bonus feat, even if she does not meet the prerequisites.																																																																																ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Mobility																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Safety in Numbers			KEY:Swarm Fighter ~ Safety in Numbers			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Fighter Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterBravery																																																																																																																												DESC:A swarm fighter benefits greatly from the proximity ofher allies. She gains a morale bonus on saves against fear effects equal to the number of allies within 20 feet ofher. This bonus can't exceed half her level.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Bonus Teamwork Feats		KEY:Swarm Fighter ~ Bonus Teamwork Feats			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Fighter Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterBonusFeat2.FighterBonusFeat6.FighterBonusFeat10.FighterBonusFeat14.FighterBonusFeat18																																																																																																															DESC:At 2nd level and every 4 levels thereafter, the swarm fighter gains a bonus Teamwork Feat.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Swarm Fighter Teamwork Feat|floor((FighterLVL+2)/4)																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Bonus Feats				KEY:Swarm Fighter ~ Bonus Feats				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Fighter Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																															DESC:At 4th level, and every 4 levels thereafter, the swarm fighter gains a bonus combat feat. These are gained as with the fighter's normal bonus feats class feature (but less frequently).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Share Space				KEY:Swarm Fighter ~ Share Space				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Fighter Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterArmorTraining1																																																																																																																											DESC:The swarm fighter can move into the space of another creature at least one size category larger than she is. She may end her movement in, and make attacks from, that space. She must succeed at the Acrobatics check for moving through an occupied square to move into a space occupied by an enemy. While sharing the space of another creature, she gains a +2 shield bonus to AC and a +1 circumstance bonus on Reflex saves.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Strike the Underbelly		KEY:Swarm Fighter ~ Strike the Underbelly			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Fighter Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterArmorTraining2																																																																																																																											DESC:Creatures with which the swarm fighter shares a space are denied their Dexterity bonus to Armor Class against the swarm fighter's attacks.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Always Underfoot			KEY:Swarm Fighter ~ Always Underfoot			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Fighter Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterArmorTraining3.FighterArmorTraining4																																																																																																																							DESC:The swarm fighter gains Step Up as a bonus feat. A creature sharing a square with the swarm fighter is considered adjacent for the purposes of this feat.	DESC: The swarm fighter gains Following Step as a bonus feat.|PREVARGTEQ:FighterLVL,17																																																							ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Step Up	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Following Step|PREVARGTEQ:FighterLVL,17																																																																																																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Soft Underbelly			KEY:Swarm Fighter ~ Soft Underbelly				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Fighter Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.FighterWeaponMastery																																																																																																																											DESC:Any attacks made against creatures with which the swarm fighter shares a space automatically confirm all critical threats.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.23

