Snare Setter			KEY:Rogue Archetype ~ Snare Setter				CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.RogueArchetype.RogueSneakAttack.RogueTrapfinding.RogueMasterStrike																																															PRECLASS:1,Rogue=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Rogue Archetype ~ Snare Setter],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.RogueSneakAttack,TYPE.RogueTrapfinding,TYPE.RogueMasterStrike]																																													DESC:Deep in darkness, the snare setter constructs his deadly traps and brutal mechanisms to confound and destroy any who try to invade his domain.																																																																								ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Snare Setter ~ Trapper|PRECLASS:1,Rogue=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Snare Setter ~ Trapsmithing|PRECLASS:1,Rogue=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Snare Setter ~ Deadly Traps|PRECLASS:1,Rogue=3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Snare Setter ~ Sneak Attack|PRECLASS:1,Rogue=5	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Snare Setter ~ Master Snare Setter|PRECLASS:1,Rogue=20																																																																																																																																										COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.23	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Rogue

Trapper				KEY:Snare Setter ~ Trapper					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Rogue Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.RogueSneakAttack																																																																																																																												DESC:A snare setter gains Learn Ranger Trap as a bonus feat. In addition to the trap granted by this feat, he learns how to construct the tripwire trap for free. For the purposes of this feat, he's considered a ranger of his snare setter level, and uses his Intelligence in place of Wisdom to determine uses per day and the DC of his ranger traps. Whenever the snare setter could learn a new rogue trick, he may instead learn a new ranger trap.																						ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Ranger Trap ~ Snare Trap	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Learn Ranger Trap																																																																																																																																																																												BONUS:VAR|TrapTimes|max(WIS+INT)-WIS	BONUS:VAR|TrapDC|max(WIS+INT)-WIS									SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Trapsmithing			KEY:Snare Setter ~ Trapsmithing				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Rogue Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.RogueTrapfinding																																																																																																																												DESC:A snare setter gains a +%1 bonus on Perception skill checks to detect traps and on Craft (traps) checks. He can use Craft (traps) in place of Disable Device to disarm traps, including magical traps.|floor(RogueLVL/2)																																																																																																																																																																																																																															BONUS:SITUATION|Perception=Trapfinding|floor(RogueLVL/2)	BONUS:SKILL|Craft (Traps)|floor(RogueLVL/2)																													SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Deadly Traps			KEY:Snare Setter ~ Deadly Traps				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Rogue Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																															DESC:The snare setter's traps deal an additional %1d6 points of damage on the first round they're activated. This damage is of the same type the trap normally deals. Traps that don't deal damage are unaffected by this ability.|min(5,floor((RogueLVL+1)/4))																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Sneak Attack			KEY:Snare Setter ~ Sneak Attack				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Rogue Class Features.SpecialAtack.Supernatural																																																																																																																																DESC:The snare setter deals +%1d6 damage with his sneak attack.|SneakAttackDice																																																																																			ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Sneak Attack																																																																																																																																																																																					BONUS:VAR|SneakAttackDice|((RogueLVL-1)/4)														SOURCEPAGE:p.23
Master Snare Setter		KEY:Snare Setter ~ Master Snare Setter			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.Rogue Class Features.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.RogueMasterStrike																																																																																																																												DESC:The snare setter can attach one of a rogue's master strike effects to a trap he creates. When the trap is triggered, the subject makes an additional Fortitude save at the same DC as the trap to avoid this effect. A snare setter can have only one trap affected by this ability active at any time. He may remove this ability from a trap at any range as a free action.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.23

